 Restrictions on major thoroughfares for goods vehicles for HS exams from 8 am to 10 am.

 Workshop

 Sananda Vatika Roopkatha, a beauty and make-up workshop, at Moksh, 22 Camac Street, 2 pm to 6 pm.

 Contest

 Elegant Anandalok Tarar Khoj at BED, 7 pm.

