 Lee Alison Sibley and Isheeta Ganguly will perform in ?Poets, dreamers and all that jazz? at Oxford Bookstore, 6.30 pm.

 Calcutta Foundation Farewell Concert at Tollygunge Club, 7.30 pm.

 Siskiyan, a majlis dedicated to Begum Akhtar, at The New Kenilworth, 8.15 pm.

